  28 Dec 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org> redland-1.0.15.ebuild,
  redland-1.0.16.ebuild, redland-1.0.17.ebuild, redland-1.0.17-r1.ebuild:
  Rename virtual/postgresql to dev-db/postgresql

  06 Nov 2014; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> redland-1.0.15.ebuild,
  redland-1.0.16.ebuild, redland-1.0.17-r1.ebuild, redland-1.0.17.ebuild:
  Require libltdl:0 specifically, and allow older libtool for stable ebuilds
  #528294 by Pacho Ramos.

